    {
      "id": "p005",
      "index": 5,
      "source": "The huge computational power of the 64 enabled Grace cores backed up by 128GB of LPDDR5 memory shows the CPU’s increasing involvement in data management for AI. Model KV-Cache offload and storage represents a third network being added to the current AI network topology of East-West (Scale-out GPU cluster scaling) and North-South (connection to storage, external resources and the Internet). With Bluefield-4, the line between a NIC with CPU compute and a CPU with networking acceleration (such as Xeon 6 SoC Granite Rapids-D) blurs even more.",
      "source_html": null,
      "element_type": "p",
      "inline_elements": [],
      "parent_block_id": "b0304",
      "parent_block_index": 304,
      "parent_block_type": "p",
      "parent_block_markdown": "The huge computational power of the 64 enabled Grace cores backed up by 128GB of LPDDR5 memory shows the CPU’s increasing involvement in data management for AI. Model KV-Cache offload and storage represents a third network being added to the current AI network topology of East-West (Scale-out GPU cluster scaling) and North-South (connection to storage, external resources and the Internet). With Bluefield-4, the line between a NIC with CPU compute and a CPU with networking acceleration (such as Xeon 6 SoC Granite Rapids-D) blurs even more.",
      "parent_block_plain_text": "The huge computational power of the 64 enabled Grace cores backed up by 128GB of LPDDR5 memory shows the CPU’s increasing involvement in data management for AI. Model KV-Cache offload and storage represents a third network being added to the current AI network topology of East-West (Scale-out GPU cluster scaling) and North-South (connection to storage, external resources and the Internet). With Bluefield-4, the line between a NIC with CPU compute and a CPU with networking acceleration (such as Xeon 6 SoC Granite Rapids-D) blurs even more.",
      "parent_source_html": null,
      "parent_inline_elements": [],
      "segment_start": 0,
      "segment_end": 544,
      "expected_tokens": [],
      "format_recovery_status": "not_applicable",
      "format_errors": [],
      "is_heading": false,
      "heading_level": null,
      "heading_chain": [],
      "is_metadata": false,
      "metadata_type": null,
      "translations": {
        "pro": {
          "text": "64 个启用的 Grace 内核搭配 128GB LPDDR5 内存，释放出庞大算力。这表明 CPU 正深度介入 AI 数据管理。当前的 AI 网络拓扑包含东西向（用于 GPU集群的横向扩展）和南北向（用于连接存储、外部资源与互联网）。模型 KV-Cache 的卸载与存储，则相当于在现有架构中新增了第三张网络。随着 Bluefield-4 的问世，具备 CPU 算力的网卡与具备网络加速能力的 CPU（如至强 6 SoC Granite Rapids-D）之间的界限愈发模糊。",
          "model": "pro",
          "created_at": "2026-04-08T16:51:12.533660",
          "tokenized_text": null,
          "format_issues": []
        }
      },
